msuffered a disappointing loss to host nationFrance, as they returned to the games for the first time in 16 years.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A feverish atmosphere at Orange Velodrome stadium inMarseilleon Wednesday, set the scene for a resounding 3-0 defeat for Marko Mitrovi\\u0107's side.\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marko_Mitrovi\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.8620685243399896, \"rank\": 0.16000000000000425, \"text\": \"Marko Mitrovi\\u0107\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marko_Mitrovi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marko_Mitrovi\\u0107\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Restricted to players under the age of 23, with an allowance for three overage players, the Olympic Men's Soccer Tournament provides some of the nation's top young talents the opportunity to face elite opposition on the world stage.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite looking in control at the beginning of the first half, and a number of close calls in the second, team USA failed to capitalize - something that was pounced on by the French.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999993167421, \"rank\": 6.833603018138543e-10, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two goals came within 10 minutes of each other, first from captain Alexandre Lacazette, who fired a low rocket into the corner from outside the box.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexandre Lacazette\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after a left-footed shot from Michael Olise from outside the box found the bottom left corner after being set up by Lacazette.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Olise\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And 15 minutes later defender Loic Bade headed home a corner kick from Joris Chotard, cementing the win for France.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_District\", \"score\": 0.8321004270824542, \"rank\": 0.20177730406352315, \"text\": \"Bade\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_District\"}, {\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joris_Chotard\", \"score\": 0.9999995922345001, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joris Chotard\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joris_Chotard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joris_Chotard\"}, {\"begin\": 1588, \"end\": 1594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.36591319827678e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 94th minute saw a chance for Griffin Young, though the goal was later ruled offside by VAR.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Griffin\", \"score\": 0.9999994238711974, \"rank\": 4.059846031670539e-07, \"text\": \"Griffin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 1688, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0524442507969063e-37, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The disappointing result for America took place in front of around 60,000 people, two days before the official Paris 2024 Opening Ceremony.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.20861163540674e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.7034305014025994, \"rank\": 0.41819248318806973, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Paralympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The game was the first meeting between the US and France at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1877, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia